Do you have the baby?

20:15.318 --> 20:16.667
The elevator!
What?!

20:16.669 --> 20:18.402
Marshall and Lily are right.
It never gets old.

20:18.404 --> 20:19.870
Unless you're crowning.

20:19.872 --> 20:21.706
So proud of you.
Thank you.

20:21.708 --> 20:23.374
Penny is proud of you.

20:23.376 --> 20:24.992
Let's go get you a brother.

20:24.994 --> 20:26.594
Okay?
Hmm?

20:26.596 --> 20:27.662
You want a brother?
All right?

20:27.664 --> 20:29.947
I love you.
I love you, too.

20:29.949 --> 20:31.115
You're gonna be great.

20:31.117 --> 20:32.266
Yeah, okay.

20:32.268 --> 20:34.885
NARRATOR:
<i>2:00 a.m., it's a good rule,</i>

20:34.887 --> 20:37.287
<i>but every rule</i>
<i>has an exception.</i>

20:37.289 --> 20:40.057
<i>And for us,</i>
<i>that exception was you, Luke.</i>

20:40.059 --> 20:41.926
We're having a baby!

20:41.928 --> 20:44.128
(yells)

20:48.901 --> 20:50.685
Come on, Trevor Hudson.

